      "**Real-world results:** Our clients typically see 75–85% of inbound calls handled fully by the AI without any human involvement. For a busy clinic or law firm receiving 50+ calls per day, that's an enormous saving in staff time — and a guarantee that no enquiry is ever missed, even outside business hours.",
      "**How is it built?** AI receptionists are powered by large language models (LLMs) fine-tuned on your business knowledge — your services, FAQs, policies, and tone of voice. They're connected to your calendar (Google Calendar, Calendly, Microsoft Bookings) and CRM via API integrations. Calls are handled through telephony platforms like Twilio or Bland AI.",
