      "**Types of marketing AI agents and what they do.** Marketing AI agents come in several forms. **Content agents** generate blog posts, social captions, and email copy based on your brand guidelines and target keywords. **Ad optimisation agents** monitor and adjust paid campaigns in real time, reallocating budget based on performance signals. **Lead nurturing agents** manage email sequences, score inbound leads, and decide when to route a prospect to your sales team. **Social monitoring agents** track brand mentions, competitor activity, and trending topics to surface engagement and content opportunities.",
